{"tid":2124752,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國泰港龍現初步確診 同層員工斥公司未即時公佈","createTime":"2020-07-25T15:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T15:40:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1b8e5b5b08c0d4ca31f8cbd60294ecec593b22","tid":2124752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200725/KNS46M7DU4EUZR7CKXK22LMO7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FKNS46M7DU4EUZR7CKXK22LMO7A%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=56a5a7c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FKNS46M7DU4EUZR7CKXK22LMO7A%2F&h=469687e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200725/KNS46M7DU4EUZR7CKXK22LMO7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n國泰港龍大廈有員工初步確診武漢肺炎，所屬辦公室昨日（24日）須全層關閉及消毒。但有員工批評國泰未有正式通知員工，亦無安排同層員工全面病毒檢測，擔心下周復工時有辦公室交叉感染。"},{"pid":"6a863c3894d92e9618d6bc4a112c05f4770a40ee","tid":2124752,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:33:01.000Z","msg":"因航玩依啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085ae3554ece49e7e47955ffc2dd3ba94ab092ff","tid":2124752,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9562db9e018727f7af3218b6e0ae625e11f53334","tid":2124752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"085ae3554ece49e7e47955ffc2dd3ba94ab092ff","tid":2124752,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/